    "headline": "Agoda Confirms \"BTS Effect\"…Travel Demand Centers on Concert Destinations",
    "summary": "Digital travel platform Agoda has witnessed a rise in travel demand to South Korea's Goyang and Busan, as well as to several destinations across APAC hosting BTS concerts, among South Korean travelers following the announcement of the K-Pop group's world tour dates. This marks BTS's first tour in four years, with fans ready to \"spring day\" into action to catch their favorite group live.",
